	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p style="text-align: center;">Calmag is the only independently owned UK manufacturer to produce a complete range of products and services to meet the needs of both domestic and commercial customers.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Calmag products offer a choice of water solutions to delivering the quality of water you want, with the added benefits of reduced energy usage and significant savings on household bills and maintenance costs. Our mission is to lead the way in innovation, protecting homes and businesses in the prevention and build up of limescale.</p>

